{"tid":2095050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[開定先] 未收到一萬蚊苦主集中問候政府專區","createTime":"2020-07-05T07:17:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T23:23:41.000Z","uid":48,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"bf6cf14705f01340581d7df354e0df8541594167","tid":2095050,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T07:17:36.000Z","msg":"原定最快7月8日「回水」一萬元的現金發放計劃，可提早至明天經銀行過數收款。政府公佈，截至前日下午5時共收到逾550萬個登記，當中約470萬個（85%）經21間參與銀行電子登記，當中透過網上理財登記接近300萬個（64%），透過銀行網站登記有約170萬個（36%）。<br />\n<br />\n財政司司長陳茂波表示，計劃過去兩星期運作暢順，由於透過網上理財登記的比例較預期高，銀行減省部份核實工序，更迅速處理登記，故6月21日至30日經銀行電子登記的約430萬名合資格人士，可提早7月6日起兩三天內經指定銀行賬戶收款。"},{"pid":"05b51f6bba8a28cbb26e5e8d1e7f002aab191b64","tid":2095050,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T07:17:59.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"2ddfdbfc6ff45c314a3bb63021dada123ab3e120","tid":2095050,"uid":48,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T07:24:14.000Z","msg":"仲有8個半鐘準備比人問候"},{"pid":"6cedcc261bf8a4c515b2e590d118dcfe4bc0fa5e","tid":2095050,"uid":6582,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T07:34:16.000Z","msg":"抽獎個d 幾時先知"},{"pid":"0e9735f566d910d1fd63f4c01ff6e3503ff2ba31","tid":2095050,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T09:45:41.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"e40c91475a3a16ac5ee46d7990c949bf5f5f6892","tid":2095050,"uid":37487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6cedcc261bf8a4c515b2e590d118dcfe4bc0fa5e","tid":2095050,"uid":6582,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T07:34:16.000Z","msg":"抽獎個d 幾時先知"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T09:47:04.000Z","msg":"有人記得先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d72869a1b7fa448d066cf923d85a2f389d945086","tid":2095050,"uid":105176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T09:48:08.000Z","msg":"屌 仲未收到 好慢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d07f